snippet: Green Bay quarterback Aaron Rodgers was injured on a sack in Monday’s loss to the Bears and does not know when he will return.
abstract: NFL Roundup; Green Bay Packers quarterback Aaron Rodgers is injured on a sack during loss to the Chicago Bears, and it remains unclear when he will return; other football news noted.

byline.original: By THE ASSOCIATED PRESS and ASHLEY SOUTHALL

lead_paragraph: Green Bay quarterback Aaron Rodgers was injured on a sack in Monday’s loss to the Bears and does not know when he will return.

headline.main: Fractured Collarbone to Keep Rodgers Out
